data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to this inviting three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom home nestled at the end of a tranquil cul-de-sac. As you step inside, the kitchen welcomes you with Corian countertops and modern stainless steel appliances, embodying a contemporary touch. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining room, and living room, enhancing the sense of spaciousness and facilitating easy interaction with loved ones. A convenient walk-in pantry provides ample storage for all your culinary essentials. Heading upstairs, you'll discover all three bedrooms, offering privacy and comfort for the entire family. The well-placed laundry room on this level adds a practical touch to your daily routine. In the backyard, a newly built deck beckons for al fresco dining and relaxation. The expansive yard opens up to open space, granting you a private retreat to enjoy nature and unwind. Embrace the peacefulness and convenience this charming abode at the end of the cul-de-sac has to offer-it's ready to welcome you home.
